description: Deletes an Amazon Web Services Migration Hub Refactor Spaces route.

parameters.name: ApplicationIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the application to delete the route from.

parameters.name: EnvironmentIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the environment to delete the route from.

parameters.name: RouteIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the route to delete.

nested_items.name: ApplicationId
nested_items.description: The ID of the application that the route belongs to.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the route.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: A timestamp that indicates when the route was last updated.

nested_items.name: RouteId
nested_items.description: The ID of the route to delete.

nested_items.name: ServiceId
nested_items.description: The ID of the service that the route belongs to.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The current state of the route.
